{"tid":625470,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"大陸果d高考作文題目好撚難","createTime":"2018-04-11T13:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T05:43:23.000Z","uid":165028,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4486140fb61cb0dddad0411252719ca3ab41e7f4","tid":625470,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"解題都有困難<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaokao.eol.cn/zuowen/jiqiao/201706/W020170607426364219040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaokao.eol.cn%2Fzuowen%2Fjiqiao%2F201706%2FW020170607426364219040.jpg&h=5d27d766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce92d4b5981554d0fedc960e049c3856bfe0d88","tid":625470,"uid":12754,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"比心機d啦"},{"pid":"f33fefbf8fd93c230459f987f192cd2383c3dd6b","tid":625470,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"全國卷I：老外眼中的中國關鍵詞<br />\n<br />\n　　（適用地區：河南、河北、山西、江西、湖北、湖南、廣東、安徽、福建）<br />\n<br />\n　　閱讀下面的材料，根據要求寫作。（60分）<br />\n<br />\n　　據近期一項對來華留學生的調查，他們較為關注的&ldquo;中國關鍵詞&rdquo;有：一帶一路、大熊貓、廣場舞、中華美食、長城、共享單車、京劇、空氣污染、美麗鄉村、食品安全、高鐵、移動支付。<br />\n<br />\n　　請從中選擇兩三個關鍵詞來呈現你所認識的中國，寫一篇文章幫助外國青年讀懂中國。要求選好關鍵詞，使之形成有機的關聯；選好角度，明確文體，自擬標題；不要套作，不得抄襲；不少於800字。"},{"pid":"141c7dd57fcb10098fe05184e8132cc71306f7c2","tid":625470,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"放低部電話啦<br />\n專心d溫書啦<br />\n<br />\n第時後悔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb59a6a04101c3c8a386ee0b48895d7cd1a356cb","tid":625470,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"不要套作點解？（最後一行）"},{"pid":"17484263ebfd30f49ca344ded74ec0a07bd905c8","tid":625470,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb59a6a04101c3c8a386ee0b48895d7cd1a356cb","tid":625470,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13: